K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-5: nga 'das nas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di la'ang byos shig /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-7: ci nas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nub par mi 'gyur zhing /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-8: ci nas khyod skyes bu tha mar mi 'gyur bar
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-9: khyod la lan gnyis lan gsum du yongs su gtad
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-10: do // rjes su yongs su gtad do //
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-12: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di 'jig
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-13: rten na ji srid du spyod pa de srid du
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-14: de bzhin gshegs pa bzhugs par rig par bya'o //

K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-18: gang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa 'di nyan pa dang /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-22: kun chub par byed pa dang /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:316b-26: kha ton du byed pa dang /

K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-1: bar byed pa'i sems can de dag ni sangs rgyas mthong ba dang ma bral pa dang /

K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-8: tshe dang ldan pa rab 'byor dang /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-9: tshe dang ldan pa sh'a ri'i bu dang /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-10: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo dang /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-14: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rang ste /
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K05D0010-3_H0012-3:317a-16: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa khri brgyad stong pa las /
